12:41.380 --> 12:46.180
like Etrus West and PK and families together

12:46.180 --> 12:51.180
to show our schools how to maximize distance learning,

12:53.300 --> 12:56.740
to find ways to support our students in distance learning,

12:56.740 --> 12:59.020
