16:08.260 --> 16:10.540
that impact our schools have been

16:11.580 --> 16:15.380
in the areas of antisemitism and Islamophobia.

16:15.380 --> 16:18.100
We intend to continue doing more webinars

16:18.100 --> 16:21.020
