29:59.140 --> 30:01.580
To seize the moment to continue our work

30:01.580 --> 30:03.860
to transform our public education system

30:04.860 --> 30:07.020
to one that is more equitable and empowering

30:07.020 --> 30:08.380
for all of our children.

30:09.220 --> 30:10.060
Thank you.

30:11.540 --> 30:14.740
And with that, we'll move to agenda item number two,

30:16.140 --> 30:17.820
